data.description: Waterfront, ocean access! Don't miss out on this fantastic pool home with its sprawling, wide open floor plan & 4+ car garage (loads of room for ALL your toys), a versatile layout that offers endless potential, no matter your needs! 5 bedrooms & 3 full baths! 3,600 sf A/C on over a half-acre with 138 ft on the wide canal! Screened lanai, pool, & a deep-water dock with lift! Home is in immaculate condition with chef's kitchen that boasts stainless steel appliances, spectacular over-sized kitchen island & quartz countertops! Pocket sliders offer the ultimate indoor/outdoor lifestyle & wide waterfront views to the South! Great location in exclusive South River Shores enclave!
